   Financial Management & Auditing Services
   FedSource can research and recoup money lost to overcharges on invoices
   from your accounts payable, telecommunications, utilities, freight and
   leasing providers. You pay nothing for the audit. The fee is only a
   percentage of the money recovered. If no errors are discovered, you are
   charged nothing for the service. Trust FedSource's private-sector
   experts to conduct your audit and recover the money you may have lost.


           Duplicate payments Unapplied discounts Unposted credits
           Various overcharges Unapplied payments Financial audits
                            (CFO Act compliance)
    Performance audits Financial statement information System review and
                                 assessment
     Internal control and financial performance Financial reporting and
                analysis Planning and performance measurement

